Location random meet people
===========================
get people to pick timeslot to meet other people
at that time and specified location (NUS) they will have to do some quirky action/activity together
possible purposes/motivation: meet friends/ speed dating/ promote healthy living/ social lives
limitation: group must be big, pranksters who fill up all the timeslots

Flow
=========
1. One master calendar, sign in with facebook
2. People select timeslots they are free 1 month in advance
3. If >50 people by 3weeks, event goes ahead. if not, event cancelled

Possible events
===============
-Freeze for 1 min at specific time
-Eat chinese food
-Play hide and seek SYSTEM ASSIGNED SEEKER  <====
-Wear green and promote green technology
-Hi 5 at least 10 strangers
